Description:
When you get to the center of the farm, a man dressed as a baker comes out of the mill and greets you.

"Hello adventurers, by any chance does your path take you to the old forest?. My son is missing, he likes to play in the forest arch but he did not return yesterday.

I would be very grateful if you could go and look for him, you can have this coins in advance."
DescriptionAction: The baker seems very desperate, maybe you can get something more out of him.
